SUMMARY:Eggstravaganza Spring Festival
DTSTAMP:20260326T215651Z
DTSTART:20260404T170000Z
DESCRIPTION:Join the City of Mill Creek for our Eggstravaganza Spring Festi
	val!  The event features a continuous egg hunt\, where children ages one t
	o eleven can search for eggs that can be exchanged for candy at multiple l
	ocations throughout the event. Enjoy photos with the Easter Bunny\, family
	 friendly activities and games! Join us for the FREE community event at th
	e Heatherwood Middle School track \\(1419 Trillium Blvd. SE\, Mill Creek\\
	). Parking is limited\, so we encourage you to walk\, bike\, or carpool.\n
	\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/eggstravaganza-spring-fest
	ival/18254710/2026-04-04T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday - Sports & Outdoors
